metadata.name: OG Collector #1/5
metadata.description:
Present from the beginning, in his hands he holds a work that represents the value of what we create. An unknown past and future are part of his trajectory without giving way to chance. His secret is to value what he acquires before acquiring it. 

For this work I painted with digital oil a static version of "Right-click and Save As guy" by XCopy in honor of him and his great contribution to the world of cryptoart. 

Dimension: 3333 x 4413px
